<lb n="2" break="no"/>nicuramuṭaiyāṟku puttūḻāṉ periyāṉ campuvarāyap pallavaraiyaṉ vaitta cantiviḷakku 1 Iccanti
<lb n="3" break="no"/>viḷakku Oṉṟukkum Ikkoyil <hi rend="grantha">śi</hi>va<hi rend="grantha">brāma</hi>ṇar kaikkoṇṭa paḻaṅkācu poṉ Ippaḻaṅkācu muṉṟuṅ ko
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṇṭu Ivviḷakku Oṉṟum cantirātittavarai Erikka kaṭavom Ikkoyil <hi rend="grantha">śi</hi>va<hi rend="grantha">brāmma</hi>ṇarom <hi rend="grantha">ḥ—</hi>
